2:56 PM - case called.  Defendant Aaron Gregory Nielsen in court.  Attorney John Zich in court for Aaron Gregory Nielsen.  Attorney Andrew R Polzin in court for State of Wisconsin. Waiver of rights and tendering plea.  Waiver free and voluntary.  Factual basis exits for plea.  Found guilty by the Court on Counts 1, 2, 3 and 4.  Joint recommendation.  Statement by Atty Polzin/Atty Zich/Defendant/Court regarding sentencing.  Court orders a fine inclusive of costs in the amount of $250.00 (total) plus cc/sc to be paid in 60 days unless payment arraignments are made with the Court.  Post conviction rights given.
